change in vulnerability to food insecurity
Difference in Hunger and Climate Vulnerability Index between 2
C global warming, for individual ensemble
In most cases, global mean changes at 2°C are larger than those at 1.5°C, not only for individual
members but also for the ensemble as a whole. All ensemble members show increases in TXx at
2°C which are larger than all changes at 1.5°C, and same true for most other variables.
